11. Conclusion
This project successfully demonstrated the complete DevOps lifecycle for a MERN stack Online Bookstore application. Starting from a simple locally-run application, we transformed it into a production-grade, cloud-native application using industry-standard DevOps tools.
Key achievements include containerizing the application with Docker, deploying it on Kubernetes with self-healing and auto-scaling capabilities, and implementing comprehensive real-time monitoring with Prometheus and Grafana with custom alert rules.
The project covers all six course outcomes: understanding containerization (CO1), demonstrating Kubernetes deployment (CO2), analyzing networking and scaling (CO3), understanding Prometheus/Grafana (CO4), executing dashboards and alerting (CO5), and evaluating automation trends (CO6).
